 Wolves</span><hr size=1> I would be very grateful and honoured if someone would see fit to sponsor me...<br><br>*casting eyes downwards*<br><br>...especially after what you all now know of me.<br><br>Please, might someone impart to me what I must do?<br><br>I eagerly await instruction.<br><br> <p>Shizandra Mysticwolf<BR>Wood Elven Druidess<BR>High Hedonist<BR> Keeper of Her Burning Heart<BR><BR>"...Darkness on the Edge...Shadows Where I Stand..."<BR><BR>"If anyone up there is listening...you know I'm not much for praying, but I don't know what else to do.  I was ready to give up once, and then she came into my life...<BR>...please...don't let that light that shines on her face go out...I couldn't stand the darkness that would follow..."</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page  <b>1</b> <a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvestunarepack.showMessageRange?topicID=260.topic&start=21&stop=25>2</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvestunarepack.showPrevMessage?topicID=260.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvestunarepack.showNextMessage?topicID=260.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvestunarepack.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=260.topic&index=20><img src=http://www.mr-bandwidth.com/aegiswolves/images/buttons/addreplybtn2.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvestunarepack.emailToFriend?topicID=260.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub7.ezboard.com/faegiswolvestunarepack.threadControl?topicID=260.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/slate/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Comm